d車，無話cut唔到"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T13:56:40.000Z","msg":"睇相對車速啦<br />\n如果大家都行緊限速<br />\n俾油咪超速囉<br />\n咁咪要收慢囉<br />\n當然我知好多人睇個路牌理解做最低車速"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T14:02:04.000Z","msg":"一早望通曬就曬大家車速黎cut, 唔係純粹超速爬頭<br />\n如果話條條線都塞車仲要左cut右cut梗係無人想讓<br />\n而且無快線撚/right lane driver就減小左好多問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d222e9db20b191972145f802f802982872e2a0cd","tid":688573,"uid":187817,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T14:08:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1f301b1b67a92532dc1b6a3591712fab88ec8365","tid":688573,"uid":38047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d222e9db20b191972145f802f802982872e2a0cd","tid":688573,"uid":187817,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T14:08:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T14:11:16.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">簡而精</span></span>"},{"pid":"d7f18ee826b542ea46e3b14391804bca53607195","tid":688573,"uid":63247,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T14:17:48.000Z","msg":"趕時間 比個5黎 <br />\n利申： 未試過有人唔讓 即使打尖都好"}]}